													#Introduction
														h1 Introduction
														p While the emotional content of daily life plays an important role in human decision-making, computers often can't understand this content. By constructing an index of emotional semantics for everyday activities, Augur enables a broader set of affective interfaces and applications.
														#IntroAPI
															h2 API
															p The Augur API is a data store of common patterns of contextual expressions and activities.
														#IntroApplications
															h2Applications
															p We demo 2 applications that leverage the capabilities of the Augur API. The first is an <strong>Smart-Scene Simulator</strong>. Given a scene of interest, such as a "temple", or a "hospital", Smart-Scene Simulator generates contextually relevant attributes of that scene. Attributes include the people in the scene, the actions they perform, and their interactions. The second application, <strong>FlowWrite</strong>, leverages the Augur API to enhance creative-writing tasks. Based on the story that is being formulated, FlowWrite provides contextually relevant ideas that contribute to generating the creative influx for writing.
												.group
