															h2 FlowWrite
															object#flowObj(type="text/html" data="http://localhost:4000/").hidden-xs.hidden-sm
															p.
																Flow Write is a novel text editor that uses data-mining to generate new associations for in-progress sentences. FlowWrite leverages the Augur API to be a design solution to generate sparks of ideas, and implement workarounds for Writer's block. Using such 'creative hinting', Flow Write accelerates creativity in writing tasks by automatically generating sentence-level ideas, allowing writers to progress faster through a story-writing task, and face fewer creative roadblocks. 
