															object#s3Obj(type="text/html" data="http://localhost:4000/game/garden").hidden-xs.hidden-sm
															p Smart Scene Simulator can generate realistic simulation environments. Simply put in a location, i.e. hospital, and watch as the scene is filled with contextually relevant groups of people, and objects.
